http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Health Education Content Standards for California Public Schools, Kindergarten Through Grade Twelve

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Standards for California Public Schools, Kindergarten Through Grade Twelve provides guidance on the essential skills and knowledge that students should have at each grade level. Local educators are encouraged to apply these standards when developing curricular and instructional strategies for health education and other interdisciplinary subjects.
